Comment: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Really, now!
Comment: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:19.90,orig,,0,0,0,,You've got a problem with that?
Comment: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Comment: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.10,orig,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:46.25,orig,,0,0,0,,Hot. That was the first thing we felt when we went down to the fifth level.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.70,orig,,0,0,0,,It should be safer there.
Comment: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.45,orig,,0,0,0,,Is this the resting area you were talking about?
Comment: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.10,orig,,0,0,0,,This used to be a Temple of Lumiaris.
Comment: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:32.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Kobolds don't worship Lumiaris, so they rarely come here.
Comment: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:03.45,orig,,0,0,0,,Do you hear something...?
Comment: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.45,orig,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Comment: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me about common sense.
Comment: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:38.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Of Michiki, Og, Mutsumi, and all their equipment,\Nonly ash remained on the ground.
Comment: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.85,orig,,0,0,0,,It will be the same for all of us.
Comment: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.70,orig,,0,0,0,,And for me?
Comment: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:24.90,orig,,0,0,0,,I can get one for one gold, but it\Ntakes time for them to grow up big.
Comment: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.55,orig,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Look out! In front of you!
Comment: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Don't have to tell me twice!
Comment: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.50,orig,,0,0,0,,You can stop.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.65,orig,,0,0,0,,That guy is out of control.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.45,orig,,0,0,0,,Hurry !
Comment: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:09.65,orig,,0,0,0,,We can't have you die too, idiot!
Comment: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Go, hurry!
Comment: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.45,orig,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you idiot!
Comment: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.95,orig,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be acting all noble.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.80,orig,,0,0,0,,You're Rantaf damn it!
Comment: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:16.75,orig,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.25,orig,,0,0,0,,Man, I sounded just like a Dark Knight just now.
Comment: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.15,orig,,0,0,0,,What, arrows?
Comment: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Hey, we should go one-on-one or something! It's cooler!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:01.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!

Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...drifted off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our princess says she's feeling weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too energetic, Og.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to stand it if you were that insensitive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going into the Cyrene Mine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The other parties are also aiming to\Nget farther in, so we can't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.70,fix,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a competition to you, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:19.90,fix,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.30,fix,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all you have to do is follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be kind of pushy, but I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He can get a little tiring sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} tired, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.10,fix,,0,0,0,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make sure to take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mutsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:04.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:09.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:34.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:37.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:40.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:43.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:47.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:54.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:04:00.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:06.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:14.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.60,fix_it,,0,0,0,,The first thing we felt when we went down to the fifth level...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.25,fix_it,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was pleasantly cool up to the fourth \Nevel, but the fifth level was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,This level was for metal smelting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and this place was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead us to a different well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can return to the fourth level from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:16.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,This level is where Merry's friends spent their last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get down from there without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can rest, but we'll need to move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to linger near the wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place we used as a resting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.60,fix,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Is this... that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.10,fix,,0,0,0,,This place used to be a Temple of Lumiaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:32.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Kobolds don't worship God, so they rarely come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...was my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.50,fix,,0,0,0,,...hear some sound...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the one who grabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Because of No Life King's curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,...they've become corpses infused with a false life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is what they look like after decaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki... Og... Mutsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time... no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry's going to the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry learned the Light Magic called Dispel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:46.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Using Lumiaris' divine protection,\Nit breaks the undead king's spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,She probably learned it knowing this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,It has a short range, so she needs\Nto get close by going to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,We can't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,It'd be no use trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo, go for the Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you get the Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru will be backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume, you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,The undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,What a sad curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,They look like people you know well, but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:25.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,What remains of their bodies no longer hold\Nmemories, and they continue to move forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,We have to let them rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohm, Rel, Ect, Nemun, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Shihoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Swat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's also a Thief, so I know his fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:58.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,It'd be a tough fight for him if he were up against\NMoguzo's heavy slashes, but against Ranta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Even I could hold off Ranta if I fought defensively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta might not be able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,These are Magic Missiles that Shihoru also uses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,I didn't know they could be used like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that skill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's doing acrobatics!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohm, Rel, Ect, Wei, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic's worn off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,One-on-one will be tough for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,I need to help them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,But how should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Dispel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mutsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume, help Moguzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll back up Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:34.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's times like these when Ranta is actually perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's changed the angles of his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'd lose against him one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:50.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Dispel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Og, I won't forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you knew what I was going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't plan it out or anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it works out, anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "common sense" only for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so nitpicky, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, so you can't help overthinking\Nthings and making them more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:34.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.90,fix,,0,0,0,,Aim carefully and try not to hit Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dispel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:32.50,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Of Michiki-san... Og-san... Mutsumi-san,\Nand all their equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.25,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.75,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Only ash remained on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:47.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,While they were alive, they felt and thought about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:57.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,About happy things, things they didn't like, things they\Nwanted to forget, and things they wanted to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,But they've died and become ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was the same for Manato, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.85,fix_it,,0,0,0,,It's the same for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally able to do what I needed to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki-san was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have more attack power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn new spells, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.70,fix,,0,0,0,,And for me, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to create an original finishing move that's just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's saying stupid things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get a wolfdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.00,fix,,0,0,0,,I can get one for one gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:24.90,fix,,0,0,0,,But it takes time for them to grow up big, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with it until it grows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll keep it in a pocket and walk around with it there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't bond with you unless you spend time with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it fit in a pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that wouldn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,I do want to get stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,...but I'd be happy just to be a stronger leader for this party.{I think he says he's fine with just party as a whole to be stronger, but I'm not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:03.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,These plain jobs are what I'm best at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a tiring day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want to hurry up and get home, so I can take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I haven't even said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.55,fix,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,H-He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Death Spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.85,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Look ahead! Ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo! War Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I— I can't do it again right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, I'll leave them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.15,fix,,0,0,0,,I know it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.50,fix,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.65,fix,,0,0,0,,That guy is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro, climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:09.65,fix,,0,0,0,,If you die... you know... it's too troublesome, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Harkiro—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you our leader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.95,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Damn Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.80,fix_it,,0,0,0,,It's not like you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta's... not coming up from this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.75,fix,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's staying below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The scaffolding gave out, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Everybody looked to me, because I'm the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:34.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,I might be incompetent, but I'm the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all die trying to save Ranta, then we'll lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But he has the devil's own luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I last saw him, he was still unharmed, so we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, will you lead us to a different\Nwell that goes to the fifth level?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go up to the third floor to recoup and go down from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Death Spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's your unlucky day, cause today you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.25,fix,,0,0,0,,Man, I sounded {\i1}very{\i0} Dark Knight-like just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.15,fix,,0,0,0,,Arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, put those down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Hey, it should be, you know, more cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Like one-on-one or som—!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:46.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,It'd be the worst if you came back to haunt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Are our enemies the kobolds?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Our real enemies are our overly weak selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:01.75,fix,,0,0,0,,Hey, come ooooon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:55.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:03.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:13.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:19.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:33.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
